title: 20 Minute Guided Run | BEGINNER FRIENDLY
description:
Here is a beginner friendly 20 minute follow along run that you can do outside or on a tread! Plug your headphones in a listen to me guide you through this 20 minute workout that will leave your body and mind feeling rejuvenated and refreshed! This is a beginner friendly run that you can do outside or on a tread! Let's get after it for the next 20 minutes, and don't forget to warm up before you begin running!!

you can take my 5 minute pre-run warmup here: 
https://youtu.be/VocwVwb_sMI

WELCOME BACK WARRIORS!!
Welcome back to my channel, or if this is your first time here, welcome to my channel! I am SO excited to announce my new 'Train With Tay' series!! I will be posting guided runs and follow-along core workouts each week so that you guys can throw some headphones on and workout anywhere at anytime!! Let me know how you guys are feeling after this run! 

#trainasyouthriveasyou #guidedruns #followalongruns #guidedworkout
channelDescription:
Hey everyone! Welcome to my YouTube channel! I’m a recently retired college athlete and current personal trainer, sharing my fitness journey and lifestyle with you. Explore my workouts, travel experiences, health tips, and daily routines as I strive to live my best life. These videos are designed to inspire and motivate you on your own fitness journey. Join me for engaging content and practical advice to enhance your health and well-being. So glad you’re here—much love!
